|CKBThe Charlatan's Working Ledger|000

Information, reputation, and gossip:

  charlhelp [topic|command]      The little black book; alias: chelp
  chskills [available]           Your trick ledger; alias: cskills
  gscore charlatan               Rank, guild XP, roads, and professions
  croads train <road>            Invest one available road point
  schemes [list|info <name>]      Inspect Rank 35+ scheme notes
  schemes learn <name>            Pay Drina to learn an open scheme
  schemes activate <name>         Fill an empty active slot at Drina
  schemes swap <old> for <new>    Pay Drina to rewrite the active loadout
  charlatan <message>            Guild line; alias: cchat
  chist [lines]                   Recent Confidence gossip
  cwho                            Visible Charlatans; alias: charlatans

Misdirection -- for marks who insist on paying attention:

  confuse [foe]
  suckerpunch [foe]              Alias: spunch
  distract [foe]
  avoid

Volatility -- chemistry with an exit strategy:

  brewacid
  brewelement <fire|ice|lightning>  Alias: elementpotion
  cookash <grey|red|blue|mixed>  Alias: ccook
  concoct <red salt|blue mixer|cutting bitters>
                                  Alias: cmix

Contraband -- improvements without warranties:

  loadweapon <weapon> with <dazzling|oiled|silvered|flaming|frozen|poisoned|shocking>
  stretchpoison <poison> onto <weapon>
  pocketsand [foe]

The caravan shops also sell ordinary throwing darts. Carry one and use
'throw <target>'. They are sharp, balanced, and entirely innocent until used.

Use 'charlhelp <command>' or 'chskills' for costs and requirements.
